main event: A UFO sighting was reported in McKinney, Texas on August 7, 1965, at 8:10 PM.
interesting points: One typical disc-shaped object was observed for 3 minutes and 20 seconds,The object appeared metallic and illuminated,The object did not make any sound,Two other observers confirmed the sighting,There had been several reported UFO sightings in the area over the past six months.
witness description: Civilian observers, including patrolmen from the police department.
